    <mxCell id="st_filter" value="&lt;b&gt;Filter Pipeline:&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;1. Recursive scan .kiro/steering/**&#10;2. Parse front-matter&#10;3. Filter: targets = langgraph | all&#10;4. Filter: inclusion = always | auto&#10;5. Sort by priority (desc)&#10;6. injectSteering() appends to&#10;   LLM system prompt" style="rounded=1;fillColor=#f3e5f5;strokeColor=#7b1fa2;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
