    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="e_hk3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;html=1;endArrow=classic;endSize=6;" edge="1" source="hk_dir" target="hk_commands" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>

    <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Summary&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;- Steering: enriches LLM system prompt (build-time for Chat, per-call for SDLC nodes)&#10;- preToolUse: intercepts before EVERY MCP call, can DENY (blocks tool execution)&#10;- postToolUse: fires after tool returns, non-blocking (log results)&#10;- agentStop: fires after each node completes (ingest output to KB)&#10;- fileEdited/Created: fires when node writes files (auto-layout drawio, lint TS)&#10;- promptSubmit: fires when pipeline receives user input (log to KB)&#10;- userTriggered: registered as VS Code commands, user clicks to execute" style="rounded=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="40" y="950" width="700" height="160" as="geometry" />
    </mxCell>

  </root>
